OL,3,CFormer football club employee spared
OL,4,Cjail for #200,000 fraud
OL,6,FA former Chelsea FC employee has been
OL,7,Fspared jail for creating false refunds
OL,8,Fon tickets to defraud the club out of
OL,9,Fmore than #200,000.
OL,11,FClaire Walsh, 39, who worked as an
OL,12,Fassistant treasury manager at the
OL,13,FPremier League football club, admitted
OL,14,Fdishonestly abusing her position to
OL,15,Fobtain #208,521.65 for herself between
OL,16,FJune 8 2019 and October 23 2023.
OL,18,FShe was sentenced to two years'
OL,19,Fimprisonment suspended for 18 months
OL,20,Fat Isleworth Crown Court on Friday.
