OL,6,FIf a Chelsea season ticket holder was
OL,7,Funable to attend a home match at
OL,8,FStamford Bridge, they could make
OL,9,Ftickets available on a club-run ticket
OL,10,Fexchange site for purchase by other
OL,11,Fseason ticket holders and club
OL,12,Fmembers, the court was told.
OL,14,FProsecutor Alex Alawode said Walsh,
OL,15,Fwhose role involved administering
OL,16,Fmanual refunds, was "creating false
OL,17,Frefunds for tickets that had not been
OL,18,Fput onto the exchange site".
