OL,4,Cjail for #200,000 fraud
OL,6,FHe added: "No tickets existed, she was
OL,7,Fsimply creating a refund as if a
OL,8,Fticket did exist on the sheet."
OL,10,FThe prosecutor said an investigation
OL,11,Festablished an "unusually high number
OL,12,Fof manual refunds on credit cards
OL,13,Festablished to be in the name of and
OL,14,Fbelonging to the defendant".
OL,16,FSentencing Walsh, Her Honour Judge
OL,17,FFiona Barrie told the defendant: "This
OL,18,Fis plainly an abuse of trust.
