OL,6,FWearing a black top and coat, Walsh
OL,7,Fcried as the suspended sentence was
OL,8,Fread out.
OL,10,FMr Alawode said Walsh, who started
OL,11,Fworking for Chelsea in 2007, told the
OL,12,Fclub that "her mother was terminally
OL,13,Fill and she had fallen into debt while
OL,14,Ftrying to provide for her family" when
OL,15,Fconfronted about the refunds.
OL,17,FWalsh was told "she could face a club
OL,18,Fdisciplinary process or immediately
OL,19,Fresign, and she decided to do the
OL,20,Flatter", the court heard.
